OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777551071
OL,3,CPlymouth bomb evacuation: Residents
OL,4,Ctold to pack bags for at least two
OL,5,Cnights
OL,7,FMore than 1,200 homes have been
OL,8,Fevacuated in the Southway area of
OL,9,FPlymouth following the discovery of a
OL,10,Fsuspected Second World War bomb.
OL,12,FWhile a lot of people who had to leave
OL,13,Ftheir homes in the evening of
OL,14,FWednesday 29 April have found shelter
OL,15,Fwith family and friends, an evacuation
OL,16,Fcentre has now been set up at Southway
OL,17,FYouth and Community Centre.
OL,19,FSince it opened, more than 25
OL,20,Fhouseholds have been placed in
OL,21,Ftemporary accommodation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/16
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777551071
OL,3,CPlymouth bomb evacuation: Residents
OL,4,Ctold to pack bags for at least two
OL,5,Cnights
OL,7,FOakwood Primary School and Little
OL,8,FAcorns PreSchool are closed, as they
OL,9,Fare both located within the 400metre
OL,10,Fsafety cordon.
OL,12,FJoyce Blackmore is one of those who
OL,13,Fhave been forced to leave their homes.
OL,15,FShe said: "Well it was a bit of a
OL,16,Fshock because first of all it was 200
OL,17,Fmetres and then when I went back home
OL,18,Fto collect a few bits this morning I
OL,19,Fhad a letter from the police saying I
OL,20,Fhad to be evacuated.
OL,26,@wD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/16
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777551071
OL,3,CPlymouth bomb evacuation: Residents
OL,4,Ctold to pack bags for at least two
OL,5,Cnights
OL,7,FI'm lucky to be able to stay with my
OL,8,Fpartner. For the ones that haven't,
OL,9,Fhaving to come to the community
OL,10,Fcentre, it's going to be a bit
OL,11,Fcrowded."
OL,13,FJoyce met her partner Bob Slough at
OL,14,Fthe community centre and they recently
OL,15,Fgot engaged.
OL,17,FMr Slough said: We've been affected by
OL,18,Fthe traffic hold ups which have been
OL,19,Fpretty horrendous. The centre has been
OL,20,Fvery helpful though, we come here
OL,21,Fregularly to play bingo and bowls."
OL,26,@sD@IO]}D@cO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/16
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
