OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777551071
OL,3,CPlymouth bomb evacuation: Residents
OL,4,Ctold to pack bags for at least two
OL,5,Cnights
OL,7,FNatasha Granville lives opposite where
OL,8,Fthe bomb is. She said: "It was a bit
OL,9,Fhectic yesterday, everyone was a bit
OL,10,Funsure of what was going to happen. We
OL,11,Fwere sound asleep when they knocked on
OL,12,Fthe door at 3am this morning so we
OL,13,Fwoke to a letter saying we had to
OL,14,Fevacuate.
OL,16,F"I work from home so it means loss of
OL,17,Fearnings, my partner has had to take a
OL,18,Fday off so we can make sure we've got
OL,19,Fsomewhere to stay for the night as we
OL,20,Fdon't have any family or friends who
OL,21,Fcan put us up.
OL,26,@pD@XOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/16
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777551071
OL,3,CPlymouth bomb evacuation: Residents
OL,4,Ctold to pack bags for at least two
OL,5,Cnights
OL,7,F"They've only just recently started
OL,8,Fconstruction there, they've started
OL,9,Fbuilding 100 or so homes there, it's
OL,10,Fthe first stages, they've only been
OL,11,Fthere a week or so, I guess they found
OL,12,Fit as they were leveling the whole
OL,13,Fplace.
OL,15,F"We could see them down tools
OL,16,Fyesterday afternoon and they started
OL,17,Fleaving last night. There were
OL,18,Fmilitary trucks arriving this morning.
OL,19,FThere are cordons everywhere, it's
OL,20,Feven been difficult to get here to the
OL,21,Fcentre today."
OL,26,@}D@NO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/16
