OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777551071
OL,3,CPlymouth bomb evacuation: Residents
OL,4,Ctold to pack bags for at least two
OL,5,Cnights
OL,7,FGiving an update on Thursday morning
OL,8,FChief Inspector Paul Laity from Devon
OL,9,F& Cornwall Police said: "I'd like to
OL,10,Fthank the public for their patience,
OL,11,Fas a city we've been here before, and
OL,12,FI know it's not ideal, but I want to
OL,13,Freassure people that public safety is
OL,14,Fwhy we're doing it.
OL,16,F"There is plenty of help from the
OL,17,Fcentre for people that have been
OL,18,Fdisplaced or are worried and it's
OL,19,Fconstantly being assessed as to what
OL,20,Fwe are doing next."
OL,26,@qD@YOUxD@AOU|D@SO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/16
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777551071
OL,3,CPlymouth bomb evacuation: Residents
OL,4,Ctold to pack bags for at least two
OL,5,Cnights
OL,7,FIt's the latest in a series of bomb
OL,8,Fdiscoveries which have brought
OL,9,Fdisruption to the centre of Plymouth.
OL,11,FTwo years ago, a 500kg Second World
OL,12,FWar German bomb was found in a garden
OL,13,Fin the Keyham area. It forced the
OL,14,Fevacuation of thousands of people and
OL,15,Fwas detonated at sea.
OL,17,FThere is a large police presence in
OL,18,Fthe Southway area and officers have
OL,19,Fbeen going door to door within the
OL,20,Fcordon to ensure people are aware they
OL,21,Fhave to leave their homes.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/16
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777551071
OL,3,CPlymouth bomb evacuation: Residents
OL,4,Ctold to pack bags for at least two
OL,5,Cnights
OL,7,FChief Inspector Laity added: "For the
OL,8,Fmost part people are taking it in
OL,9,Ftheir stride, we know it's a lot of
OL,10,Fupheaval, we've asked people to pack
OL,11,Fbags for at least two nights and we
OL,12,Fknow that's a real inconvenience and
OL,13,Fthat's why we thank them for what they
OL,14,Fare doing, it's just to keep them safe.
OL,16,F"We learn every time from these
OL,17,Fincidents, the learning all goes back
OL,18,Finto the pot and hopefully it runs as
OL,19,Fsmoothly as it can."
OL,26,@oD@^OUxD@AOU{D@TO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/16
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777551071
OL,3,CPlymouth bomb evacuation: Residents
OL,4,Ctold to pack bags for at least two
OL,5,Cnights
OL,7,FSpecialist enhanced Xray equipment
OL,8,Fhas now arrived on site, allowing
OL,9,FRoyal Navy UXO experts to continue
OL,10,Ftheir detailed assessment of the
OL,11,Fdevice.
OL,13,F400 tonnes of sand has been delivered
OL,14,Fto the site which is being used by
OL,15,Fspecialists to build a mitigation
OL,16,Fstructure to help stabilise and secure
OL,17,Fthe device while assessment continues.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/16
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777551071
OL,3,CPlymouth bomb evacuation: Residents
OL,4,Ctold to pack bags for at least two
OL,5,Cnights
OL,7,FOfficials say they are aware that a
OL,8,Fsmall number of residents are asking
OL,9,Fif they can return to their homes to
OL,10,Fcollect essential items such as
OL,11,Fmedication. Unfortunately, the clear
OL,12,Fadvice from the Royal Navy is that no
OL,13,Fone should reenter the cordon at this
OL,14,Ftime.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/16
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777551071
OL,3,CPlymouth bomb evacuation: Residents
OL,4,Ctold to pack bags for at least two
OL,5,Cnights
OL,7,FPlymouth City Council said in a
OL,8,Fstatement: "The current safety cordon
OL,9,Fremains at 400 metres. Whilst we
OL,10,Fcannot guarantee that the cordon won't
OL,11,Fbe extended further, any decision to
OL,12,Fdo so would be based solely on advice
OL,13,Ffrom the Royal Navy UXO specialists.
OL,15,F"At this stage, no request or decision
OL,16,Fhas been made to extend the cordon
OL,17,Ffurther. Therefore, any suggestion
OL,18,Fthat the cordon is definitely being
OL,19,Fexpanded beyond 400 metres is
OL,20,Fspeculation.
OL,26,@pD@LOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/16
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777551071
OL,3,CPlymouth bomb evacuation: Residents
OL,4,Ctold to pack bags for at least two
OL,5,Cnights
OL,7,F"We understand that people are keen to
OL,8,Fknow what will happen next, including
OL,9,Fwhether the cordon will be extended,
OL,10,Fwhen and how the device will be made
OL,11,Fsafe. At this time, we need to be
OL,12,Fhonest and say that we simply don't
OL,13,Fyet know.
OL,15,F"Royal Navy UXO specialists are still
OL,16,Fcarrying out a detailed assessment of
OL,17,Fthe device, which includes bringing in
OL,18,Fspecialist equipment. We are hopeful
OL,19,Fthat we will know more later today and
OL,20,Fwill share updates as soon as that
OL,21,Finformation becomes available.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/16
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777551071
OL,3,CPlymouth bomb evacuation: Residents
OL,4,Ctold to pack bags for at least two
OL,5,Cnights
OL,7,F"What we do know is that the
OL,8,Fspecialists have advised that a
OL,9,F400metre cordon must be fully
OL,10,Fevacuated to allow them to work
OL,11,Fsafely. We recognise that some people
OL,12,Fare understandably anxious about
OL,13,Fleaving their homes, but this advice
OL,14,Fhas been given solely to protect
OL,15,Fresidents and keep people safe."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/16
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777551071
OL,3,CPlymouth bomb evacuation: Residents
OL,4,Ctold to pack bags for at least two
OL,5,Cnights
OL,7,FCouncillor Sally Haydon from Plymouth
OL,8,FCity Council said: "We are saying to
OL,9,Fpeople in the cordon, please leave
OL,10,Fyour home, come with your medication,
OL,11,Fif you have dogs bring some dog food,
OL,12,Fanything you need.
OL,14,F"If you've got nowhere to go please
OL,15,Fcome to the Southway Community Centre
OL,16,Fand we can try and help with
OL,17,Faccommodation.
OL,26,@pD@TOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/16
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777551071
OL,3,CPlymouth bomb evacuation: Residents
OL,4,Ctold to pack bags for at least two
OL,5,Cnights
OL,7,F"It's obviously a challenge, but the
OL,8,Fcity is ready, we've had experience
OL,9,Ffrom the last two we've had so we're
OL,10,Fable to use that plan and adapt to the
OL,11,Farea, never forgetting there are
OL,12,Fresidents behind this and making sure
OL,13,Fthey are safe and they are
OL,14,Fcomfortable."
OL,16,FThere were more than 50 Luftwaffe air
OL,17,Fraids on Plymouth between 1941 and
OL,18,F1944, killing 1,174 civilians in the
OL,19,Fcity.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/16
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
