FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777551071
OL,3,CPlymouth bomb evacuation: Residents
OL,4,Ctold to pack bags for at least two
OL,5,Cnights
OL,7,FThe first bombs fell on the city on
OL,8,FJuly 6 1940 with the heaviest period
OL,9,Fof bombing occurring in March and
OL,10,FApril 1941.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/16
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
